WEBVTT

00:08:59.723 --> 00:09:02.559
Ili hadithi zako zisomwe na kusikika.

00:09:02.583 --> 00:09:05.338
Jaribu tu kujitahidi polepole na fantasia

00:09:05.362 --> 00:09:07.816
ambayo itakuponya,

00:09:07.840 --> 00:09:11.924
itajaza mashimo ya chizi ya Uswisi ndani yako.

00:09:11.948 --> 00:09:13.542
haiwezekani.

00:09:13.566 --> 00:09:14.926
haitokuwa.

00:09:14.950 --> 00:09:16.655
Lakini uandishi unaweza.

00:09:16.679 --> 00:09:20.277
Pia unaweza kuimba kwenye kwaya
au bendi.

00:09:20.301 --> 00:09:23.608
Pia uchoraji au ufugaji wa ndege

00:09:23.632 --> 00:09:26.800
au kukuza mbwa wazee ambao hakuna mtu mwingine anataka.

00:09:28.570 --> 00:09:31.621
Ya nane: familia.